'''《油脂》'''（{{lang-en|''Grease''}}，又名-{zh-cn:《火爆浪子》、《青春狂热》;zh-hk:《火爆浪子》、《青春狂熱》;zh-tw:《油脂》、《青春狂熱》;zh-sg:《油脂》、《火爆浪子》}-）是[[美國|美國]]作曲家{{link-en|吉姆·雅各布斯|Jim Jacobs}}和{{link-en|沃倫·凱西|Warren Casey}}於1971年創作的[[音樂劇|音樂劇]]。该剧以1950年代美國工人階級出身的青少年亞文化{{link-en|油脂者|Greaser (subculture)|油脂者}}命名，敘述了在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]一間虛構高中韋迪爾高中（原型為公立高中{{link-en|威廉·霍華德·塔夫脫高中 (芝加哥)|William Howard Taft High School (Chicago)|威廉·霍華德·塔夫脫高中}}<ref name="Debate plays on for Chicago guitarist's induction into Taft High School's Hall of Fame: Group wants late guitarist added to school hall of fame">{{Cite news| last = Defiglio| first = Pam| title = Debate plays on for Chicago guitarist's induction into Taft High School's Hall of Fame: Group wants late guitarist added to school hall of fame| newspaper = Chicago Tribune| pages = | date = 2009-02-19| url = http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2009/feb/19/local/chi-terry_kath_city_zonefeb19| accessdate = 2009-11-27| quote = Alumni honored in Taft's Hall of Fame include ... Jim Jacobs, who based his musical "Grease" on Taft High School Jupe.| archive-date = 2010-03-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100322234628/http://archives.chicagotribune.com/2009/feb/19/local/chi-terry_kath_city_zonefeb19| dead-url = no}}</ref>）的十名高中生探索對朋輩壓力、政治、個人核心價值和愛情的疑惑。剧中歌曲重現了1950年代的[[搖滾|搖滾]]風格。《油脂》在芝加哥首演后被贬为一部不修边幅、具攻擊性和低俗的音樂劇，但其後的製作減少了有關內容<ref name="Grease Essay">{{cite web|last=Miller|first=Scott|title=Inside Grease|publisher=New Line Theatre|date=2007-03-30|url=http://www.newlinetheatre.com/greasechapter.html|accessdate=2008-07-10|archive-date=2008-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081003025529/http://www.newlinetheatre.com/greasechapter.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《油脂》反映了[[未成年懷孕|青少年懷孕]]、[[童黨|童黨]]等社會問題。它的主題亦包含愛情、友誼、[[青少年犯罪|青少年犯罪]]、青春期時的[[人類的性|性爆發]]，以及[[階級意識|階級意識]]和[[階級鬥爭|階級鬥爭]]。

《油脂》在1971年於芝加哥金士顿矿业剧院首次公演<ref name="Grease Returns to Its Raunchy Roots">{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/features/article/grease-returns-to-its-raunchy-roots-177793|title=Grease Returns to Its Raunchy Roots|first=Robert|last=Simonson|date=2011-03-31|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518084624/http://www.playbill.com/features/article/grease-returns-to-its-raunchy-roots-177793|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並于1972年6月7日在[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓中城|曼哈頓中城]]的{{link-en|布罗德赫斯特剧院|Broadhurst Theatre}}公演<ref name="《GREASE火爆浪子》歷史">{{cite web|url=http://www.grease2014.com/#!introduction/c1gn9|title=《GREASE火爆浪子》歷史|accessdate=2015-04-09|work=樹德科技大學|publisher=樹德科技大學|date=2013-09-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415205749/http://www.grease2014.com/#!introduction/c1gn9|archivedate=2015-04-15}}</ref>。《油脂》现已成為史上最成功的音樂劇之一。直至1980年落幕，它共在百老匯演出了3388次<ref name="《GREASE火爆浪子》歷史" />，打破了《[[屋顶上的提琴手|屋顶上的提琴手]]》3242場的公演紀錄，成為[[百老匯|百老匯]]公演次數最多的音樂劇，直至1983年被《[[歌舞線上|歌舞線上]]》打破，但截至2015年4月仍為百老匯第十五最多公演場數的音樂劇<ref>[http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/75222.html "Long Runs on Broadway"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/75222.html |date=20090420212111 }} Playbill.com, 2011-08-14</ref>。《油脂》在1973年6月在倫敦首演時<ref name="《GREASE火爆浪子》歷史" />，亦曾經揚威[[倫敦|倫敦]][[西區劇院|西區劇院]]，並在1978年改編成[[油脂_(電影)|電影]]。《油脂》亦是中學話劇團、區域劇院和社區劇院較常演出的劇目之一<ref>根據2008年5月26日出版之《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》第51頁 , 《油脂》在2007年成為美國高中最常演出的音樂劇之一</ref>。

==製作歷史==
===製作背景===
1959年，[[搖滾音樂|搖滾音樂]]開始在美國盛行<ref name="Grease Essay" />。而性自由亦逐步開放<ref name="Grease Essay" />，至1970年代更掀起性革命<ref name="Grease Essay" />。加上受當時美國反戰浪潮，以及同類音樂劇《{{link-en|咖啡邦戈|Expresso Bongo}}》、《[[毛髮_(音樂劇)|毛髮]]》等的影響<ref name="Grease Essay" />，《油脂》便在這個浪潮之下應運而生<ref name="Grease Essay" />。

===1971年芝加哥版和1972年百老匯版===
[[File:Broadhursttheatre.jpg|left]]
《油脂》的創作背景源自編劇之一吉姆·雅各布斯在母校威廉·霍華德·塔夫脫高中的回憶<ref name="Debate plays on for Chicago guitarist's induction into Taft High School's Hall of Fame: Group wants late guitarist added to school hall of fame" />。沃倫·凱西其後加入與吉姆·雅各布斯共同創作。

《油脂》在1971年於芝加哥{{link-en|林肯大道 (芝加哥)|Lincoln Avenue (Chicago)|林肯大道}}的金士顿矿业剧院首次公演<ref name="Grease Returns to Its Raunchy Roots" />。製片人{{link-en|肯·韋斯文|Ken Waissman}}和玛克辛·福克斯在收看芝加哥公演之後，與編劇達成協議，取得《油脂》在[[外百老匯|外百老匯]]的製作權和公演權<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1997-11-24/features/1997328050_1_waissman-grease-corner-symphony|title=A new musical from the 'Grease' guy Theater: Baltimore-born Kenneth Waissman took a show to Broadway 25 years ago, and tonight he ushers 'Street Corner Symphony' into the limelight.|first=J. Wynn|last=Rousuck|date=1997-11-24|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151022033108/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1997-11-24/features/1997328050_1_waissman-grease-corner-symphony|dead-url=no}}</ref>。製作團隊於是由芝加哥遷到紐約，以集中在《油脂》紐約版的製作。《油脂》紐約版由{{link-en|湯姆·摩爾 (導演)|Tom Moore (director)|湯姆·摩爾}}執導，{{link-en|帕特里夏·伯奇|Patricia Birch}}編舞（其後她亦參與電影版的編舞工作，並執導其{{link-en|油脂2|Grease 2|續集}}），1972年2月14日在[[曼哈頓下城|曼哈頓下城]]的伊頓劇院公演<ref name="playbillvault">{{cite web|url=http://www.playbillvault.com/Show/Detail/2031/Grease|title=Grease|publisher=Playbill Vault|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425012435/http://www.playbillvault.com/Show/Detail/2031/Grease|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然地理上當時《油脂》在外百老匯公映，但其製作已達到百老匯水準<ref>{{cite book|last=Guernsey|first=edited by Otis L.|title=The Best plays of 1971–1972|url=https://archive.org/details/bestplaysof1971100otis|year=1972|publisher=Dodd, Mead|location=New York|isbn=0-396-06698-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/bestplaysof1971100otis/page/492 492]}}</ref>，因此該劇在{{link-en|第二十六屆東尼獎|26th Tony Awards}}中獲得7項提名<ref name="playbillvault" />。

1972年6月7日，《油脂》遷至百老匯{{link-en|布罗德赫斯特剧院|Broadhurst Theatre}}公演<ref name="playbillvault" />，再在同年11月21日遷至{{link-en|伯纳德·B·雅各布剧院|Bernard B. Jacobs Theatre|皇家劇院}}公演<ref name="playbillvault" />，並在該劇院一直公演至1980年1月27日<ref name="playbillvault" />。在公演最後五週，《油脂》再遷往座位更多的[[美琪剧院|庄严剧院]]公演<ref name="playbillvault" />，直至1980年4月13日落幕<ref name="playbillvault" />。由在百老匯首演至落幕起計，《油脂》共進行3388次公演<ref name="playbillvault" />。

1972年百老匯首演時的演員陣容包括{{link-en|巴里·博斯特威克|Barry Bostwick}}（飾演丹尼）、{{link-en|卡罗尔·德马斯|Carole Demas}}（飾演桑迪）、{{link-en|阿德里安娜·巴博|Adrienne Barbeau}}（飾演里索）、{{link-en|蒂莫西·迈耶斯|Timothy Meyers}}（飾演肯力基）、{{link-en|艾倫·保羅|Alan Paul}}（飾演青年天使和莊尼·加西諾）、{{link-en|沃尔特·伯比|Walter Bobbie}}（飾演羅傑）、{{link-en|繆思·斯摩|Mews Small}}（飾演法蘭奇）<ref>{{cite web|title=Photo Coverage: Original Broadway Cast of GREASE Reunites at GYPSY OF THE YEAR|date=2011-12-07|first=Walter|last=McBride|url=http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Photo-Coverage-Original-Broadway-Cast-of-GREASE-Reunites-at-GYPSY-OF-THE-YEAR-20111207|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505021209/http://www.broadwayworld.com/article/Photo-Coverage-Original-Broadway-Cast-of-GREASE-Reunites-at-GYPSY-OF-THE-YEAR-20111207|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。其後出演百老匯版《油脂》的演員包括{{link-en|杰夫·科纳韦|Jeff Conaway}}（後在電影版飾演肯力基）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/jeff-conaway-kenickie-in-grease-film-dies-at-60-179612|title=Jeff Conaway, Kenickie in "Grease" Film, Dies at 60|first=Robert|last=Simonson|date=2011-05-27|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090517/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/jeff-conaway-kenickie-in-grease-film-dies-at-60-179612|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|盖尔·爱德华兹|Gail Edwards}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gailedwards.com/|title=Gail Edwards • Theatrical headshots throughout the 70's and 80's|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429104326/http://www.gailedwards.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|馬利盧·亨納爾|Marilu Henner}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=71729|title=Marilu Henner|publisher=Internet Broadway Database|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402155505/http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=71729|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[彼得·蓋勒|彼得·蓋勒]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.petergallagher.org/biography/|title=Peter Gallagher - Biography|accessdate=2015-05-02|archive-date=2015-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150507081157/http://www.petergallagher.org/biography/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|艾琳·格拉夫|Ilene Graff}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibdb.com/person.php?id=88014|title=Ilene Graff|publisher=Internet Broadway Database|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505040516/http://www.ibdb.com/person.php?id=88014|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|朱迪·凯|Judy Kaye}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=47553|title=Judy Kaye|publisher=Internet Broadway Database|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318083130/http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=47553|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[柏德烈·史域斯|柏德烈·史域斯]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000664/bio|title=Patrick Swayze Biography|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150313090105/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0000664/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[尊·特拉華特|尊·特拉華特]]（後在電影版飾演男主角丹尼）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbillvault.com/Person/Detail/42668/John-Travolta|title=John Travolta|publisher=Playbill Vault|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505055256/http://www.playbillvault.com/Person/Detail/42668/John-Travolta|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|杰里·扎克斯|Jerry Zaks}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playbill.com/features/article/a-life-in-the-theatre-jerry-zaks-171340|title=A Life in the Theatre: Jerry Zaks|first=Mervyn|last=Rothstein|date=2010-09-01|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2016-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160121172400/http://www.playbill.com/features/article/a-life-in-the-theatre-jerry-zaks-171340|dead-url=no}}</ref>、{{link-en|特依特·威廉姆斯|Treat Williams}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001852/bio|title=Treat Williams Biography|publisher=IMDb|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617065322/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001852/bio|dead-url=no}}</ref>等。而[[李察·基爾|李察·基爾]]亦在此次公演中成為替補演員，他在此次公演的角色包括男主角丹尼、青年天使和文斯·方丹<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ibdb.com/person.php?id=41996|title=Richard Gere|publisher=Internet Broadway Database|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403190028/http://www.ibdb.com/person.php?id=41996|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===1973年西區劇院版===
《油脂》在1973年6月在倫敦西區劇院的[[新倫敦劇院|新倫敦劇院]]公演<ref name="《GREASE火爆浪子》歷史" />，由當時仍未成名的李察·基爾擔演男主角丹尼。而倫敦首次公演中的其他演員包括斯泰西·格雷格（飾演桑迪）、斯蒂芬·本特（飾演羅傑）、杰奎 - 安·卡尔（飾演里索）、德里克·詹姆斯（飾演杜迪）等。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=ZWIRAljCR7oC&pg=PA160&lpg=PA160&dq=grease+1973+london+cast+New+london+theatre&source=bl&ots=EdVqVPWVCc&sig=pt2r21bdKnkgyDhQ1py-F0Z80Do&hl=en&ei=pqpyTJCsMoTGlQfbwomhDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CDEQ6AEwCDg8#v=onepage&q=grease%201973%20london%20cast%20New%20london%20theatre&f=false|author=Green, Stanley|title='Grease', London, 1973|work=Encyclopedia of the Musical Theatre|publisher=Da Capo Press|year=1980|ISBN=0-306-80113-2|page=160|access-date=2015-04-27|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704023424/http://books.google.com/books?id=ZWIRAljCR7oC&pg=PA160&lpg=PA160&dq=grease+1973+london+cast+New+london+theatre&source=bl&ots=EdVqVPWVCc&sig=pt2r21bdKnkgyDhQ1py-F0Z80Do&hl=en&ei=pqpyTJCsMoTGlQfbwomhDg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=9&ved=0CDEQ6AEwCDg8#v=onepage&q=grease%201973%20london%20cast%20New%20london%20theatre&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Hepple, Peter|url=http://www.glenncarter.com/stage/musicals/grease.htm|title='Grease' history glenncarter.com (from ''The Stage'')|date=2002-10-10|accessdate=2011-08-26|archive-date=2011-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110727023931/http://www.glenncarter.com/stage/musicals/grease.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>其後，{{link-en|保罗·尼古拉斯|Paul Nicholas}}、[[伊莲·佩姬|伊莲·佩姬]]取代李察·基爾和斯泰西·格雷格擔演主角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.agathachristie.com/news/article/and-then-there-were-none-takes-to-the-stage|title=AND THEN THERE WERE NONE TAKES TO THE STAGE|publisher=Agatha Christie|accessdate=2015-05-05|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617214545/http://www.agathachristie.com/news/article/and-then-there-were-none-takes-to-the-stage|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1979年第二次公演時，則由{{link-en|苏·波拉德|Su Pollard}}和[[特蕾西·厄尔曼|特蕾西·厄尔曼]]出演主角<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.londontheatredirect.com/post/437/Which-departed-London-shows-should-come-back-to-the-West-End-.aspx|title=BLOGS:Which departed London shows should come back to the West End|publisher=London Theatre Direct|date=2012-06-19|accessdate=2015-05-04|archive-date=2015-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151227202706/https://www.londontheatredirect.com/post/437/Which-departed-London-shows-should-come-back-to-the-West-End-.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

